<h1 id='payschedule-documentation'>Payschedule Documentation</h1><h2 id='create'>Create</h2>
<ul>
<li>Path: <code>/payschedule/weekly/create</code></li>
<li>HTTP Verb: POST</li>
<li>Schema:
<code>
{
&quot;day_of_week&quot;: 4 // Sunday is 0, Saturday is 6
}
</code></li>
<li>Response: 
<code>
{
&quot;id&quot;: 1,
&quot;day_of_week&quot;: 4,
&quot;current_period_id&quot;: 7,
&quot;employer_id&quot;: 4
}
</code></li>
</ul>
<h2 id='add-employee-to-payschedule'>Add Employee to Payschedule</h2>
<ul>
<li>Path: <code>/payschedule/weekly/add-employee</code></li>
<li>HTTP Verb: POST</li>
<li>Schema: See sidebar</li>
</ul>
